OL,3,C'Young people and black workers at
OL,4,Chighest risk of workplace surveillance'
OL,6,FYoung people new to the labour market
OL,7,Fand black employees are among the most
OL,8,Flikely to be subject to surveillance
OL,9,Fin the workplace, according to a
OL,10,Freport.
OL,12,FShop floor staff, warehouse workers,
OL,13,Fdelivery drivers, and those working in
OL,14,Fcall centres and from home are all at
OL,15,Fhigh risk of having calls recorded,
OL,16,Femails analysed and possibly even
OL,17,Fbeing monitored by cameras or laptop
OL,18,Fwebcams, a think tank said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
