OL,3,C'Young people and black workers at
OL,4,Chighest risk of workplace surveillance'
OL,6,FArtificial intelligence (AI) is has
OL,7,Ftransformed surveillance, he added,
OL,8,Fgiving employers an even greater
OL,9,Finsight into their employees.
OL,11,FHe said: "Surveillance and algorithmic
OL,12,Fmanagement are very linked. Often
OL,13,Fsurveillance packages are single
OL,14,Fsoftware packages which both collect
OL,15,Fdata and then use it to make
OL,16,Frecommendations to employers, and
OL,17,Falgorithmic management itself is being
OL,18,Finnovated and rapidly transformed by
OL,19,FAI which can create much more
OL,20,Fsophisticated insights."
