OL,3,C'Young people and black workers at
OL,4,Chighest risk of workplace surveillance'
OL,6,FIncreasing levels of surveillance of
OL,7,Fcertain workers could "deepen the
OL,8,Finequalities already baked into the
OL,9,Flabour market", said Mr Evans, noting
OL,10,Fthat black workers are more likely to
OL,11,Fbe in jobs with a higher risk of
OL,12,F"intrusive surveillance".
OL,14,FHe added that productivity could also
OL,15,Fbe affected.
OL,17,F"If surveillance has a chilling effect
OL,18,Fon people's willingness to express
OL,19,Fthemselves in the workplace, that may
OL,20,Falso decrease their satisfaction at
OL,21,Fwork," he said.
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@NO]tD@AOUtD@XO]yD@AOU}D@FO]
