OL,6,FThe IPPR analysed data from the 2023
OL,7,FInstitute for Social and Economic
OL,8,FResearch's UK Household Longitudinal
OL,9,FSurvey to produce its findings.
OL,11,FA Department for Business and Trade
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "Our plan to Make
OL,13,FWork Pay aims to ensure workers'
OL,14,Frights keep pace with technological
OL,15,Fchange so that workers' voices are at
OL,16,Fthe heart of Britain's digital
OL,17,Ftransition.
OL,19,F"This includes safeguarding against
OL,20,Finvasion of privacy and discrimination
OL,21,Fby algorithms."
